# Patch 41.8.1 Release Note

This is a HOTFIX patch release to address the following issue, which can cause the loss of file resources linked to tracker events and tracked entity attributes

- **[DHIS2-21427](https://dhis2.atlassian.net/browse/DHIS2-21427): File resources for tracker events / TEAVs deleted by DATA_VALUE_TRIM job**  
    Components: _[API] File Resources_
    
See [Patch 42.3.0](ReleaseNote-2.41.8.md) for the full list of fixes included in the parent patch release.
